1. Check if you have nodejs installed( Npm on windows is bundled with nodejs)
2. Check if create-react-app is there if not install it globally using -g 
	npm install -g create-react-app 

3. once create-react-app is installed create a new application 
	create-react-app <your-app-name> 

4.  cd <your app> 
	npm start 


